!!Logging into a REST server
A [[TiddlyWiki5 plugin|https://github.com/OokTech/TW5-Login]] for logging into a REST server to get an access token. This plugin adds the `$login-widget`, which lets you login to servers that use token authentication. It sends (using an HTTP POST) a username and password to a url and expects an access token in reply.

